metadata.name: Green palace
metadata.description:
The Green Palace is one of the places that I have depicted based on my interests and feelings of a place that I would like to see in reality.
Because to relax the mind, one must travel to beautiful places, a dreamy trip, a trip without the distance of time and space.
close your eyes and focus on where you want to be right now, How good you would have felt? Now life's problems are not a complex mystery for you...
